org.sql: SELECT SUM(issues.estimated_hours) FROM issues INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = issues.project_id WHERE issues.root_id = "$1" AND issues.lft >= 88 AND issues.rgt <= 95 AND projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'issue_tracking') IS NOT NULL AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (6, 13)) AND issues.is_private = False
